OL,5, Children's author and illustrator      
OL,6, Shirley Hughes has died aged 94, her   
OL,7, family has confirmed.                  
OL,9,FHughes was best known for creating the 
OL,10,FAlfie book series, as well as          
OL,11,Fchildren's picture book Dogger.        
OL,13,FShe died "peacefully at home after a   
OL,14,Fshort illness" on Friday in London, her
OL,15,Ffamily told the PA news agency.        
OL,17,F"Shirley's books about everyday family 
OL,18,Flife are adored by generations of      
OL,19,Ffamilies and she is held in the highest
OL,20,Festeem by her peers," they said.       
